title: Nemesis.1992.BDRip.1080p.OriginalAudio.EngSub.OST
description:
Remux of the cyberpunk Nemesis film from 1992. This remux has the following

- Untouched video from the iFPD torrent
- Original multi-channel AC-3 audio from the DVD - narrated by Jared (thanks to manbungo for the audio)
- Bluray multi-channel AC-3 audio - narrated by Alex
- English soft subs (thanks to manbungo for the subs)
- Complete OST of the film added as an extra

Enjoy :)
